experiences.description: Stepping up into a junior coordinator role, I had more oversight over the junior program enabling me to better tailor the training program to younger athletes. I also stepped into a manager role as I helped to develop the coaches around me to better communicate with their athletes.

Through my employment here I worked on a variety of projects. Initially I was employed as a web developer, making changes to multiple Shopify stores to improve both functionality and aesthetics with the help of an Asana task board. This role then expanded into backend application building, namely a shipping calculator that interacted with the Shopify API to provide shipping rates. I also gained experience scripting in Ruby and React JS through Shopify scripts and maintained the Force USA app respectively.
Received Google Data Analytics Professional Certificate.
